<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">اللَّهُ عَنْهُ قَالَ:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">آخِرُ سُورَةٍ نَزَلَتْ:</span> <span class="c4">[بَرَاءَةَ]</span>.<span class="c5"> وَآخِرُ آيَةٍ نَزَلَتْ:</span> ﴿يَسْتَفْتُونَكَ قُلِ اللَّهُ يُفْتِيكُمْ فِي الْكَلالَةِ﴾.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
